### Framework 12 – Rotation Fix
#   Problem:
#   Rotation incorrectly detected in tablet mode.
#
#   Hardware:
#        Framework 12
#        Sensor: KIOX000A
#
#   Solution:
#   hwdb entry added:
#       61-framework12.hwdb
#
#   Entry:
#   mapping for the framework12 sensor
#   
#   Test status:
#       ✓ KDE Wayland
#
# Kernel version: 6.19.11.arch1-1
sensor:modalias:acpi:FRMWC004*:dmi:*
 ACCEL_MOUNT_MATRIX=0, 1, 0; -1, 0, 0; 0, 0, 1